longBusinessSummary: Value Grupo Financiero, S.A.B. de C.V. provides various financial services. It provides brokerage, credit, operational and financial leasing, factoring, stock market intermediary, and other services. The company was formerly known as Grupo Financiero Fina Value SA de CV and changed its name to Value Grupo Financiero, S.A.B. de C.V. in May 2000. Value Grupo Financiero, S.A.B. de C.V. was incorporated in 1992 and is based in San Pedro Garza García, Mexico.
